---
title: Spanish-Style Cod with Chickpeas over Zucchini and Arugula
description: Have you ever been awakened by the smell of paprika-infused cod while taking a siesta on a beach in Spain? Us neither! But it sounds delightful. Our guest chef André from HelloFresh UK had that very experience when he was on vacation. He’s recaptured that bit of magic by the Spanish seashore in a recipe that features a dusting of smoked paprika, a flaky cod fillet, and a warm, cumin-y jumble of zucchini and chickpeas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w21-r3-81111d17.jpg
